    <thetext>For Local Task, the URL attribute in the Attribute section seems to determine the width of the task.
So for long URLs unexpected horizontal scrollbars are added.

h4. Steps to Reproduce

* Create new local tasks
* Enter very long URL into the URL attribute
* Press Ctrl-S to save
** Expected result: The width of the URL field stays the same.
** Actual result:
*** The URL field expands to the left to accomodate the complete URL.
*** A horizontal scroll bar is added to the bottom since the complete task widget gets much wider.

